# Project Context

React 19 portfolio with GSAP + Lenis animations. Pure CSS (no Tailwind), no TypeScript.

# Coding Standards

1. All animations in `/src/hooks/useGSAP.js` - add to `initAnimations()`
2. GSAP cleanup required: `ScrollTrigger.getAll().forEach(t => t.kill())`
3. Animate only `opacity` and `transform` (GPU-accelerated)
4. Lenis must sync with GSAP ticker (already configured in useGSAP)

# File Structure

- Single-page pattern: all sections in `App.jsx`
- All styles in `index.css` using CSS custom properties
- Do not modify `main.jsx`
